        alias='primaryItemGroupType',
        description='The item group type. Supported value: <code>SELLER_DEFINED_VARIATIONS</code>, indicates that the item group was created by the seller. <br><br>When you create your code, ensure that your app gracefully handles any future changes to this list.<br><br><div class="msgbox_important"><p class="msgbox_importantInDiv" data-mc-autonum="&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #dd1e31;&quot; class=&quot;mcFormatColor&quot;&gt;Important! &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;"><span class="autonumber"><span><b><span style="color: #dd1e31;" class="mcFormatColor">Important!</span></b></span></span> This field no longer returns values and is scheduled for deprecation.</p></div>',
